</emphasis>
(designated by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDF18C20B3EFFF3FEFEBC6E9453AEB7" author="Taylor, N. P." box="[366,530,377,399]" pageId="47" pageNumber="72" pagination="110 - 120" refId="ref18292" refString="Taylor, N. P. (1995) The Sesse and Mocino cactus platres - A postscript Bradleya 13: 110 - 120. https: // doi. org / 10.25223 / brad. n 13.1995. a 11" type="journal article" year="1995">Taylor 1995: 119</bibRefCitation>
